	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">OUTSIDE OF BATTLE CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Select command / Select location / Increase or decrease buying and selling amount:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Select action / Advance text window / Speed up cursor (world map):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Cancel action / Close window:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Close window / Jump to end for wanzer name menu:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Move world map camera (used with Directional Pad):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Switch selected pilot / Switch selected Colosseum combatant:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 or R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Open help section:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Skip text:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">VIEW MODE CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move camera:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Zoom in:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Zoom out:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Exit view mode:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Return camera to original position:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">NETWORK CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move cursor / Select command / Increase or decrease buying and selling amount(BURG/ONSET only):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Select action / Advance text window/input characters:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Cancel action / Backspace one character:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Jump to End for Input menus:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Toggle HP indicators ON or OFF(E.BIRD only):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Switch selected forum/switch selected article(DNC/DOCTRAL only)/rotate map by 45 degrees(E.BIRD only).:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 or R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Open Help section(BURG/ONSET and E.BIRD only):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Skip text/end map analysis(E.BIRD only).:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">IN BATTLE CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move cursor / Select command:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Confirm command / Open command window / Advance text window:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Cancel command / Close command window / Advance text window / Speed up Player and Enemy Phase text:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Hide Weapon Status window / Toggle Free Cursor Mode(used to freely move around and access any unit's data on the battlefield, only for Semi-Auto Control settings):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Toggle HP indicators ON or OFF / Toggle Honor indicators ON or OFF / Hide Weapon Status window:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Rotate map by 45 degrees:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 or R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Switch selected unit / Switch selected square:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L2 or R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Open Unit List menu:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L2 + R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Open Help section:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Open system window / Skip text:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br><br>
        &nbsp;</td>
	 </tr>
